snippet.title: The Horrible Journey Of Amber Heard In Aquaman 2 Starts Soon....
snippet.description:
Filming of Aquaman 2 starts very very soon and so a lot is about to happen in terms of Amber Heard Versus the world. It's going to get crazy, so let's talk about what we can all expect over the next few years.
